NAC domain containing protein 1: Homeodomain-like protein with RING/FYVE/PHD-type zinc finger domain

miPEP165a is an 18 amino acid peptide encoded by the primary transcript of miR165a.Application of miPEP165a increased the accumulation of miR165a transcripts and acts at the level of transcription. It is expressed in the root endodermis. Over expression leads to an increase in root length.
